action hero biju is a 2016 indian malayalam-language drama film directed and co-written by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; shine in his second directorial venture . the movie chronicled the real professional life of an ordinary police officer , the film stars nivin pauly in the title role of police inspector biju &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , a &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; with the kochi city police . nivin pauly , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; shine and shibu &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; produced the film under the banners pauly jr pictures and full on studios . the film is written by muhammad &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and shine . jerry amaldev composed the original songs , while rajesh murugesan composed the background score . principal photography began in may 2015 and ended in october 2015 . after being postponed several times , action hero biju was released in kerala on 4 february 2016 and rest of india on 5 february 2016 . the film became a commercial success .